WINDOWS
=======

Open and build the solution in Visual Studio 2019 or later, or open a PowerShell or Command Prompt window, navigate to the ude folder and type:

    $ dotnet build
    $ dotnet test
    
LINUX
=====

In your favourite shell, navigate to the ude folder and type:

    $ dotnet build
    $ dotnet test
   
MAC OS
======

Open and build the solution in Visual Studio for Mac, or open Terminal, navigate to the ude folder and type:

    $ dotnet build
    $ dotnet test
   
ALL PLATFORMS
=============

To run the example program, type:

    $ dotnet run <path to file to test> --project src/Example

